name: salownik-agh.pl
description:
Project of an application aimed at making it easier for the AGH UST students to find the appropriate room in which they will have classes. Searching by number, you can get a lot of information that will help you get to the right room.


Supposedly driven by user-generated content.

Each user will be able to add a new room the database.


(the design lacks mobile version - to be added)


App currently under development.
